      "assistant": {
        "Response": {
          "message_id": "cda1d37a-595e-4f40-af11-e96a2b42678f",
          "content": "Spec is ready (`a9486ba`). Four trust levels:\n\n- **3 owner** — aksika via TG DM → full authority\n- **2 self** — KP's own observations → act freely (default for extractions)\n- **1 peer** — A2A agents → non-destructive only, ask owner for anything dangerous\n- **0 untrusted** — open web → never act, only report\n\nKey defense rules: untrusted content can never trigger actions, peer content can't trigger destructive ops without your confirmation, and trust can never be escalated by the content itself (anti prompt injection).\n\n9 implementation tasks. Want to start building it?"
        }
      },
