                          "title": "Multilevel security",
                          "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multilevel_security",
                          "snippet": "Because all information in an MLS environment is physically accessible by the OS, strong logical controls must exist to ensure that access to information is strictly controlled. Typically this involves mandatory access control that uses security labels, like the Bell–LaPadula model.",
                          "publishedDate": 1773748922000,
                          "id": "1",
                          "domain": "wikipedia.org",
                          "maxVerbatimWordLimit": -1,
                          "publicDomain": false
                        },
                        {
                          "title": "Want Trustworthy Agentic AI Systems? Do This First.",
                          "url": "https://builtin.com/articles/agentic-ai-data-governance",
                          "snippet": "Summary: Agentic AI offers autonomous operations, yet its independence requires rigorous data governance to prevent costly errors. By prioritizing data classification, access control, lineage and lifecycle management, leaders ensure these reasoning engines act predictably and remain compliant at scale.",
                          "publishedDate": 1772636400000,
                          "id": "2",
                          "domain": "builtin.com",
                          "maxVerbatimWordLimit": 30,
                          "publicDomain": true
                        },
