                          "url": "https://www.weforum.org/stories/2026/03/ai-agent-autonomy-governance/",
                          "snippet": "The expanded autonomy and memory of AI agents across interlocking systems creates new vulnerabilities and security imperatives. Responsible governance of AI agents means defining the extent of their capabilities according to the particular context in which they operate.",
