                          "url": "https://federalnewsnetwork.com/artificial-intelligence/2026/03/as-military-ai-divide-widens-heres-one-path-for-agentic-systems/",
                          "snippet": "Summary: AIA says agentic AI could unlock faster, more adaptive decisions across the defense industrial base, but only if agencies and contractors address risks and real‑world friction. The conversation is unfolding as policymakers debate how military AI should be governed and what limits are necessary.",
