                          "snippet": "Defense giants xAI and IBM are unleashing specialized AI models designed for classified military ops - not just general-purpose LLMs. These systems, built for air-gapped networks and strict IL5 security, empower 3 million+ personnel with real-time insights while locking down data access via RBAC and 180-day audit logs.",
