    "All 600 tests pass. Here's the summary:\n\n**Job 2 (Todo List) — Done:**\n- Task 2.1: `src/cli/agentbridge-todo.ts` — `add`, `list`, `done`, `remove` commands, writes to `~/.agentbridge/memory/todo.md`\n- Task 2.2: `skills/todo/SKILL.md` — steering for the agent\n- Task 2.3: Deploy wiring in `scripts/deploy.sh`\n\n**Job 3 (Internal Cron) — CLIs + Skills done, heartbeat integration pending:**\n- Task 3.1: `src/cli/agentbridge-cron.ts` — `add`, `list`, `remove` commands, writes to `~/.agentbridge/memory/cron.json`\n- Task 3.5: `skills/cron/SKILL.md` — steering for the agent\n- Task 3.6: Deploy wiring in `scripts/deploy.sh`\n\n**Still pending from Job 3:**\n- Task 3.2: Heartbeat cron checker (read cron.json every 5min, fire due entries)\n- Task 3.3: Pending reminders pickup (inject fired reminders into conversation)\n- Task 3.4: Task subagent + TG report (spawn kiro-cli for task-type cron entries)\n\nWant me to continue with Tasks 3.2–3.4 (the runtime integration)?\n[Tool uses: none]",
