    "Everything works. Here's the summary:\n\n**Browser Subagent — Complete (6 tasks)**\n\n| File | What |\n|------|------|\n| `persona/browsing_prompt.md` | Template with `${TASK}`, `${CHAT_ID}`, `${TIMESTAMP}`, `${BROWSER_STATUS}` — full browser tool instructions |\n| `src/cli/agentbridge-browse.ts` | CLI: parses args, loads template, spawns detached kiro-cli, writes `pending_browse.json`, returns immediately |\n| `src/components/cron-checker.ts` | Added `checkBrowseTasks()` — checks pid alive/dead/timeout, delivers results via `pending_reminders.json` |\n| `src/main.ts` | Wired `checkBrowseTasks()` into 5-min interval + startup |\n| `skills/browse-delegate/SKILL.md` | Tells professor: NEVER run browser commands directly, always use `agentbridge-browse` |\n| `scripts/deploy.sh` | CLI wrapper, skill steering, prompt template deployment |\n| `src/cli/agentbridge-browse.test.ts` | 8 tests: arg parsing, validation, template loading |\n| `src/components/browse-checker.test.ts` | 5 tests: dead pid, timeout, alive, missing file, graceful fallback |\n\n**61 test files, 633 tests, all passing.** Build clean.\n[Tool uses: none]",
