default 5min), `--dry-run`> \n- Load `browsing_prompt.md` template, replace variables> \n- Spawn detached `kiro-cli acp --agent professor` with the prompt piped via stdin or as first message> \n- Log subprocess output to `~/.agentbridge/logs/browse_<taskId>.log`> \n- Write task metadata to `~/.agentbridge/memory/pending_browse.json` (taskId, chatId, pid, startedAt, timeoutMs)> \n- Print `{ \"ok\": true, \"taskId\": \"...\", \"status\": \"spawned\" }` and exit immediately> \n- Follow same patterns as agentbridge-sleep.ts (parseArgs, invokeSubagent, audit)> \n> \n**Task 3: Create browse task checker + result delivery**> \n- New function `checkBrowseTasks()` in `src/components/cron-checker.ts`> \n- Reads `pending_browse.json`, for each entry:> \n  - If pid dead: read log file tail (500 chars), write result to `pending_reminders.json` as `🌐 Browser task completed: <task>\\n\\n<result>`, remove from pending_browse.json> \n  - If pid alive but past timeout: kill pid, report timeout> \n  - If pid alive and within timeout: skip> \n- Wire `checkBrowseTasks()` into the existing 5-min interval in main.ts (alongside `checkCron()`)> \n> \n**Task 4: Create `skills/browse-delegate/SKILL.md` steering for professor**> \n- Tells professor: \"for ANY browser task, call `agentbridge-browse --task '...' --chat-id <ID>` — NEVER run agentbridge-browser or docker exec commands directly\"> \n- Explains the async pattern: call returns immediately, result delivered later> \n- Keep existing `skills/browser/SKILL.md` unchanged (the browser subagent uses it directly)> \n- Deploy new skill in `scripts/deploy.sh`> \n> \n**Task 5: Tests**> \n- `src/cli/agentbridge-browse.test.ts`:> \n  - Arg parsing: missing --task errors, missing --chat-id errors, valid args parsed correctly> \n  - Dry-run mode prints prompt to stdout> \n  - Template loading and variable replacement> \n- `src/components/browse-checker.test.ts`:> \n  - Dead pid → result delivered to pending_reminders.json, entry removed from pending_browse.json> \n  - Timed-out pid → killed, timeout reported> \n  - Still-alive pid within timeout → left alone> \n  - Missing/empty pending_browse.json → no crash> \n  - Missing log file → graceful fallback message> \n> \n**Task 6: Deploy wiring**> \n- `scripts/deploy.sh`: add `agentbridge-browse` CLI wrapper + symlink (same pattern as todo/cron)> \n- `scripts/deploy.sh`: add `browsing_prompt.md` deployment to `~/.agentbridge/`> \n- `scripts/deploy.sh`: add `skills/browse-delegate/SKILL.md` → `~/.agentbridge/.kiro/steering/browse-delegate.md`> \n- Build + full test suite green (620+ tests)",
