    "\n\nThat's much cleaner — let Dreamy handle it as part of the sleep cycle instead of a separate cleanup script. The agent already reads through messages during sleep; it just needs instructions to prune the garbage while summarizing.\n\nLet me check what the sleeping prompt currently says about message handling:\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
