    "Here's the integration test result:\n\n**Pre-sleep:** 626 messages (318 user, 308 assistant)\n**Post-sleep:** 614 messages (311 user, 303 assistant)\n\n| Action | Count |\n|--------|-------|\n| Immediate deletes (dupes + wrong chat) | 12 messages |\n| Garbage marked (7-day grace) | 104 messages |\n| FTS integrity | ✅ in sync (614 = 614) |\n\nAfter the 7-day grace period expires, the next sleep cycle would delete those 104 garbage-marked messages, bringing the total down to **510 messages** (~18% reduction).\n\nNo data corruption, FTS stays in sync, `chat_backup` untouched. Want me to commit the updated test script?\n[Tool uses: none]",
