    "\n\nYeah, that was way too much work for a subagent — I dumped the entire GC protocol on it and it probably got stuck scanning 626 messages one by one.\n\nLet me try a leaner approach — give the subagent a focused, bounded task instead of the whole §3:\n[Tool uses: execute_bash]",
