15m\n  🔌 Transport: TMUX — ✅ Connected\n  💓 Heartbeat: running (5min)\n  📋 Tasks: sleep-trigger\n  😴 Last sleep: sleep_20260316_083012.md\n  ```\n- Apply to both Telegram (line ~522) and Discord (line ~1131)\n\nTest: existing tests unaffected\n\nDemo: `/status` in Telegram shows full system overview\n\n**Task 3: Cleanup**\n\nObjective: Remove `getCronInfo()` from MemoryManager if no longer needed elsewhere, or keep it since `/status` still uses it. Remove `getTaskNames()` from HeartbeatSystem if unused.\n\n- Actually both are still used by `/status` → keep them\n- No cleanup needed\n\n**Task 4: Commit and push**\n\n---\n\nDoes this plan look good, or would you like me to adjust anything?\n[Tool uses: none]",
