    "No \"Reaction\" log entries at all — the `logInfo(\"main\", `Reaction ${emojis}...`)` line never fired. The bridge hasn't seen any `message_reaction` updates from Telegram. Two possibilities:\n\n1. **The bridge was restarted after the deploy** — the like was sent before the new code was running\n2. **Telegram `allowed_updates: []` quirk** — empty array means \"use previously saved settings\", NOT \"all types\". If the bot was first polled without `message_reaction` in the list, Telegram remembers that.\n\nLet me check when the bridge last started:\n[Tool uses: execute_bash]",
