    "Összefoglaló a memory audit-ról:\n\n| Funkció | As-built | Valóság | Státusz |\n|---------|----------|---------|---------|\n| recordMessage (SQLite+JSONL) | ✅ | ✅ működik | OK |\n| Chat save (10min idle) | ✅ | ✅ Mar 17, 18 saves | OK |\n| Heartbeat ticks | ✅ 5min | ✅ 30min (1 task only) | OK |\n| Startup sleep | ✅ | ✅ (de nem volt restart 2 napja) | OK |\n| Cron sleep | ✅ | ❌ wrong path, silently fails | **FIXED** (`9af615b`) |\n| Consolidation (working→daily) | ✅ via sleep | ❌ no sleep = no consolidation | Fixed by sleep fix |\n| GC (7-step) | ✅ via sleep | ❌ same | Fixed by sleep fix |\n| MemoryExtractor (heartbeat) | ✅ in doc | ❌ removed in code (Mar 9) | As-built stale |\n| Reaction scoring | ✅ | ✅ wired | OK |\n| agentbridge-recall | ✅ | ✅ agent uses it | OK |\n| agentbridge-store | ✅ | ✅ agent uses it | OK |\n\nDeploy kell, és utána a cron sleep holnap reggel ≥8am-kor automatikusan lefut. A `spawnedToday` flag resetelődik restart-nál, szóval ha deploy-olsz ma, a startup sleep is lefut.\n[Tool uses: none]",
