    "This session:\n\n1. **FTS5 sanitization** — studied OpenClaw + lossless-claw approaches, simplified agentbridge's `sanitizeFtsQuery` from blacklist to quote-wrapping (LCM pattern). Committed `99e8251`.\n\n2. **PowerPoint MCP integration** — researched options, installed `office-powerpoint-mcp-server` via pipx, registered in mcporter with `lifecycle: keep-alive`, discovered the `presentation_id` requirement, added steering file to agentbridge, added daemon start to launcher script. Commits `2905d5e`, `a3e6567`.\n\n3. **Standalone pptx-creation project** — created `~/workspace/pptx-creation/` with steering, templates/data/output dirs for native kiro-cli testing without agentbridge.\n\nPrior session: sleep startup >25h fix, lossless-claw comparison, 5-recommendation LCM enhancement plan saved to `docs/TODO/lcm-enhancements.md`.\n[Tool uses: none]",
