    "All done. Here's the full summary:\n\n**Stage 1** (`5645075`): Schema + recall tracking + CLI flags\n**Stage 2-4** (`95a2efd`): Ranking boost + compression stats + full sleep cycle restructure\n**Docs** (`5bac930`): All 18 tasks marked complete\n\n3 unpushed commits. 651/651 tests pass. Remind me when you want to push (you might want to run the full suite yourself first).\n\nWhat was implemented:\n- 5 new columns on `extracted_memories` (recall_count, last_recalled_at, relevance_score, confidence, source_message_ids)\n- Every `agentbridge-recall` search bumps recall_count on extracted memory hits\n- Search ranking: `(bm25 + emotion) × (1 + 0.1×recall) × (1 + 0.2×relevance)`\n- CLI: `--confidence`, `--source-ids`, `--boost/--demote --id`, `--merge --merge-ids`\n- Sleep snapshot: compression ratio + Darwinism stats\n- Sleep prompt: 9 sections (§1 Feedback → §2 Summary → §3 Reminders → §4 GC → §5 Cron → §6 Topics → §7 Fitness → §8 Merge → §9 Disk)\n[Tool uses: none]",
    "> did we implement the whole plan, missing anything?",
