    "\n[Tool uses: fs_write]",
    "Here's the plan and skill. Review `docs/TODO/memory-confidentiality.md` for the implementation tasks and `skills/classification/SKILL.md` for the agent rules.\n\nKey design decisions:\n- ISO 27001 terms: public / internal / confidential / restricted\n- `restricted` is a one-way door — agent can escalate into it but never out\n- Only `--user-override` CLI flag can declassify restricted (human-in-the-loop)\n- Restricted memories are excluded at the SQL level (`WHERE classification <= ?`) — not just agent behavior\n- Sleep agent also capped at `confidential` — restricted never enters consolidation/merge\n\n9 tasks total. Want to discuss anything or shall I build?\n[Tool uses: none]",
