  "latest_summary": [
    "\n\n## OBJECTIVE\nBuild and enhance the agentbridge memory system with Darwinism (recall tracking, relevance scoring, fitness-based pruning), LCM-inspired enhancements (source linking, expand CLI, large message interception), and ISO 27001 memory confidentiality classification.\n\n## USER GUIDANCE\n- Write only the ABSOLUTE MINIMAL amount of code needed\n- User communicates in Hungarian/English mix, code/docs in English\n- All data must stay local, no cloud services\n- Don't run full test suite unless user explicitly says so\n- When staging git commits, exclude unrelated `ToDo/` → `docs/TODO/` renames (stale working tree state)\n- `src/cli/agentbridge-store.ts` uses CRLF line endings — use python for multi-line edits, not sed\n\n## COMPLETED\n\n### Memory Darwinism — All Stages Done\n- **Stage 1** (`5645075`): 5 new columns (`recall_count`, `last_recalled_at`, `relevance_score`, `confidence`, `source_message_ids`), `bumpRecallCount()`, `adjustRelevance()`, CLI flags (`--confidence`, `--source-ids`, `--boost`, `--demote`)\n- **Stages 2-4** (`95a2efd`): Ranking boost formula, compression stats, sleep cycle restructured to §1-§9, `mergeMemories()`, `--merge --merge-ids`\n- **Source IDs read path** (`96984b9`): `source_message_ids` in SELECT + JSON output\n- **Docs** (`e0391d6`): 15/18 tasks done, 3 deferred → later completed to 17/18\n- **Tests** (`d2c8f63`): 18 Darwinism tests — bumpRecallCount, adjustRelevance, mergeMemories, instantStore, searchExtracted ranking, parseArgs\n\n### LCM Enhancements — All Stages Complete\n- **Stage 1 Tasks 1-2**: source_message_ids column + `--source-ids` CLI (merged into Darwinism)\n- **Stage 1 Task 3** (`b521959`): Recall expand hints — stderr hint when results have source_message_ids\n- **Stage 1 Task 4** (`b521959`): `agentbridge-expand --ids <csv>` CLI — reads original messages from `messages` table by ID, JSON output. Guard: `isMain` check so tests can import without side effects. 3 parseArgs tests.\n- **Stage 1 Task 5**: `--source-ids` in sleep template GC examples\n- **Stage 2+3**: Done prior (sleep retry + bootstrap reconciliation)\n- **Stage 4**: Merged into Darwinism sleep template restructure\n- **Stage 5** (`6d64e1b`): Large message interception — `src/components/message-interceptor.ts`. `interceptLargeMessage(text, threshold=8000)`: if over threshold, writes full content to `~/.agentbridge/overflow/overflow_<ts>.md`, returns truncated preview (500 chars) + file path. Wired into 3 `sendPrompt` paths in main.ts (Telegram line ~927, Discord line ~1515, B2B line ~1085). 4 tests.\n\n### Memory Confidentiality — ISO 27001 Classification (`cb2296e`)\n- **Schema**: `classification INTEGER DEFAULT 1` on `extracted_memories` (idempotent ALTER TABLE)\n- **Levels**: 0=public, 1=internal (default), 2=confidential, 3=restricted/secret\n- **Store**: `--classification 0-3` on agentbridge-store, passed through InstantStoreParams\n- **Reclassify**: `--reclassify --id N --classification L` on agentbridge-store. `reclassifyMemory(id, level, userOverride=false)` on MemoryManager enforces R2: restricted (3) cannot be lowered without `--user-override`\n- **Search filtering**: `COALESCE(em.classification, 1) <= ?` in both `searchExtracted()` and `searchOriginal()`. `maxClassification` capped at 2 via `Math.min(opts?.maxClassification ?? 2, 2)` — restricted ALWAYS excluded even if caller passes 3\n- **Recall**: `--max-classification 0-2` flag on agentbridge-recall, passed to searchOpts\n- **Sleep prompt**: §4 GC has classification rule, §7 Fitness query excludes `WHERE classification < 3`\n- **Skill file**: `skills/classification/SKILL.md` — auto-trigger rules (user says \"secret\", token patterns like `sk-`, `ghp_`, `Bearer`, `-----BEGIN`), context-based disclosure rules, examples\n- **Tests**: 8 new in darwinism.test.ts — restricted excluded from search, maxClassification=0 only public, maxClassification=3 still excludes restricted, reclassify between 0/1/2 allowed, reclassify restricted→lower blocked, user-override bypass works\n- **AES encryption** saved to Future Ideas in Memory.asbuilt.md (`a406f8e`)\n\n### KP's Manual Edit (not yet in source)\nKP (the user's agent \"Kiro Persona\") manually updated the deployed `~/.agentbridge/.kiro/steering/memory-search.md` to document `source_message_ids` output field and `agentbridge-expand` usage. The source `skills/memory-search/SKILL.md` may not have this update yet — needs review and sync.\n\n## TECHNICAL CONTEXT\n\n### Project Root\n`/mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/`\n\n### Key Files Modified This Session\n- `src/components/memory-manager.ts` — 6 ALTER TABLE migrations (added `classification`), `reclassifyMemory()`, `instantStore()` now accepts `classification` param\n- `src/components/memory-index.ts` — `searchExtracted()` and `searchOriginal()` accept `maxClassification` in opts, add `COALESCE(em.classification, 1) <= ?` WHERE clause\n- `src/types/memory.ts` — `InstantStoreParams` has `classification?: number`\n- `src/cli/agentbridge-store.ts` — CRLF file. RawArgs has `classification`, `reclassify`, `userOverride`. parseArgs handles `--classification`, `--reclassify`, `--user-override`. Main function has reclassify path before boost/demote path. validateArgs passes classification.\n- `src/cli/agentbridge-recall.ts` — `maxClassification` in parseArgs, passed to searchOpts and searchOriginal\n- `src/cli/agentbridge-expand.ts` — NEW. `parseArgs(argv)` exported. `isMain` guard for CLI entry. SELECT from `messages` WHERE id IN (...).\n- `src/components/message-interceptor.ts` — NEW. `interceptLargeMessage(text, threshold=8000)` exported. Uses `AGENT_BRIDGE_HOME` from config.ts for overflow dir.\n- `src/main.ts` — imports `interceptLargeMessage`, calls it before `sendPrompt` in 3 paths\n- `persona/sleeping_prompt.md` — §4 GC classification rule, §7 Fitness query excludes restricted\n- `skills/classification/SKILL.md` — NEW. Agent classification rules and auto-triggers.\n- `src/components/darwinism.test.ts` — 26 tests total (18 Darwinism + 8 classification)\n- `src/components/message-interceptor.test.ts` — 4 tests\n- `src/cli/agentbridge-expand.test.ts` — 3 tests\n\n### Ranking Boost Formula\nSQL: `rank * (1.0 + 0.1 * COALESCE(em.recall_count, 0)) * CASE WHEN COALESCE(em.relevance_score, 0) > 0 THEN 1.2 ELSE 1.0 END ASC`\nJS: `(bm25Score + emotionBoost) * (1 + 0.1 * recall_count) * (1 + (relevance_score > 0 ? 0.2 : 0))`\n\n### Classification Filter\nSQL: `COALESCE(em.classification, 1) <= ?` where param = `Math.min(maxClassification ?? 2, 2)`\n\n### Git Status\nAll commits pushed through `b521959`. Unpushed:\n- `6d64e1b` feat: large message interception\n- `cb2296e` feat: memory confidentiality — ISO 27001 classification\n- `a406f8e` docs: add AES encryption for restricted memories to Future Ideas\n\n### Test Status\n- Last targeted run: 26/26 darwinism.test.ts, 4/4 message-interceptor.test.ts, 3/3 agentbridge-expand.test.ts\n- Last full run: 65/65 files, 676/676 tests all green (one earlier flaky run showed 1 failure that passed on retry)\n\n## TOOLS EXECUTED\n- Multiple `npm run build` — all clean\n- `npm test src/components/darwinism.test.ts` — 26/26 pass\n- `npm test src/components/message-interceptor.test.ts` — 4/4 pass\n- `npm test src/cli/agentbridge-expand.test.ts` — 3/3 pass\n- Full test suite: 65/65 files, 676/676 tests pass\n- `git push` — pushed through `b521959`\n- `./scripts/deploy.sh` — deployed successfully\n- Git commits: `d2c8f63`, `9ff0988`, `6d64e1b`, `b521959`, `cb2296e`, `a406f8e`\n\n## NEXT STEPS\n1. **Review KP's memory-search skill update** — compare deployed `~/.agentbridge/.kiro/steering/memory-search.md` with source `skills/memory-search/SKILL.md`, sync the expand/source_message_ids documentation back to source\n2. **Push unpushed commits** (`6d64e1b`, `cb2296e`, `a406f8e`)\n3. **Deploy** — run `scripts/deploy.sh`\n4. **Update instant-store skill** — add `--classification` parameter documentation to `skills/instant-store/SKILL.md`\n\n## TODO LIST\nID if loaded: none\n\n## FACTUAL RECORD\n\n### Files Modified and Read\n_(Most frequently and recently accessed first. Indented items show summaries for the last 5 modifications.)_\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/main.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/darwinism.test.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/cli/agentbridge-recall.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/memory-manager.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/persona/sleeping_prompt.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/memory-index.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/docs/TODO/lcm-enhancements.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/docs/specs/Memory.asbuilt.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/cli/agentbridge-store.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/types/memory.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/skills/classification/SKILL.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/docs/TODO/memory-confidentiality.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/cli/agentbridge-expand.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/cli/agentbridge-expand.test.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/message-interceptor.test.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/message-interceptor.ts\n* /home/qakosal/.agentbridge/.kiro/steering/memory-search.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/skills/memory-search/SKILL.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/skills/instant-store/SKILL.md\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/persona\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/memory-db.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/config.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/b2b-router.ts\n* /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/src/components/conversation-buffer.ts\n\n### Commands Executed\n_(Showing 17 of 36 commands, most frequently and recently executed first)_\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && npm run build 2>&1 | tail -5 - Build check\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && npm test -- --silent 2>&1 | tail -8 - Full test suite\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && npm test src/components/darwinism.test.ts 2>&1 | tail -15 - Run darwinism + classification tests\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && git push - Push all commits\n* find ~/.agentbridge/ -name \"*memory*search*\" -o -name \"*recall*\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 - Find deployed recall/memory files\n* find ~/.agentbridge/ -name \"SKILL.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -10 - Find any deployed skills\n* find ~/.agentbridge/ -name \"SKILL.md\" -path \"*memory*\" 2>/dev/null - Find deployed memory skill\n* diff /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge/skills/memory-search/SKILL.md ~/.agentbridge/skills/memory-search/SKILL.md 2>&1 || echo \"Files d... - Compare source vs deployed skill\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && git add docs/specs/Memory.asbuilt.md && git commit -m \"docs: add AES encryption for restricted ...\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && git commit -m \"feat: memory confidentiality — ISO 27001 classification (public/internal/confide... - Commit classification feature\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && git diff --cached --stat - Verify staged changes\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && git reset HEAD ToDo/ docs/TODO/BACKLOG.md docs/TODO/comet-browser-evaluation.study.md docs/TODO... - Unstage stale ToDo renames\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && git add -A && git diff --cached --stat - Check staged changes\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && npm test src/components/darwinism.test.ts 2>&1 | tail -5 - Run tests\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && npm run build 2>&1 | tail -3 - Final build check\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open(\"docs/TODO/memory-confidentiality.md\", \"r\") as f:\n    content = f....\n* cd /mnt/c/Users/qakosal/workspace/agent/agentbridge && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open(\"docs/TODO/memory-confidentiality.md\", \"r\") as f:\n    content = f.... - Mark all tasks done\n",
